{"sn45.36:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 45.36 ","sn45.36:0.2":"4. Patipattivagga ","sn45.36:0.3":"Dutiyasamannasutta ","sn45.36:1.1":"Savatthinidanam. ","sn45.36:1.2":"“Samannanca vo, bhikkhave, desessami, samannatthanca. ","sn45.36:1.3":"Tam sunatha. ","sn45.36:1.4":"Katamanca kho, bhikkhave, samannam? ","sn45.36:1.5":"Ayameva ariyo atthangiko maggo, seyyathidam—","sn45.36:1.6":"sammaditthi …pe… sammasamadhi. ","sn45.36:1.7":"Idam vuccati, bhikkhave, samannam. ","sn45.36:1.8":"Katamo ca, bhikkhave, samannattho? ","sn45.36:1.9":"Yo kho, bhikkhave, ragakkhayo dosakkhayo mohakkhayo—","sn45.36:1.10":"ayam vuccati, bhikkhave, samannattho”ti. ","sn45.36:1.11":"Chattham. "}